    <title>JQuery面向对象写法</title>
    <link href="https://crazy-boy.github.io/archives/JQuery%E9%9D%A2%E5%90%91%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1%E5%86%99%E6%B3%95.html"/>
    <id>https://crazy-boy.github.io/archives/JQuery面向对象写法.html</id>
    <published>2018-04-19T01:52:00.000Z</published>
